import math

def calculate_word_combinations(consonants, vowels):
    f = math.factorial
    total_letters = consonants - vowels
    consonant_combinations = f(7) // (f(consonants) * f(7 - consonants))
    vowel_combinations = f(5) // (f(vowels) * f(5 - vowels))
    total_combinations = consonant_combinations * vowel_combinations * f(total_letters)
    return total_combinations
